original_title: 3 Blickwinkel - Königsklasse im Herzen von Europa
overview: From the relegation battle to winning the Europa League to the Champions League anthem for the first time - Eintracht Frankfurt has experienced turbulent times with incredible moments. We have accompanied the SGE on their journey to the Champions League so far - and we were in the heart of Europe.
title: 3 Blickwinkel - Königsklasse im Herzen von Europa
